[SPEAKER_00] Sve bio, međutim, nema tko da si te...

302
00:25:05,900 --> 00:25:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sve to postoji.

303
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nema tko reći avionima da lete.

304
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:11,759
[SPEAKER_00] Nema tu su glasnosti to je.

305
00:25:11,759 --> 00:25:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] i nema odobrenja,

306
00:25:13,980 --> 00:25:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] nema te snage da dobiješ diplomatko zeleno tijekom.

307
00:25:17,500 --> 00:25:19,839
[SPEAKER_01] Da se donese odluka i da se provede odluka.

308
00:25:19,839 --> 00:25:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] Apsolutno.

309
00:25:20,599 --> 00:25:22,019
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je to...

310
00:25:22,019 --> 00:25:22,740
[SPEAKER_01] Taj cijeli...

311
00:25:22,740 --> 00:25:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je cijela, sva ta priča,

312
00:25:25,099 --> 00:25:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] to je za Hrvatsku vrlo opasna priča,

313
00:25:27,500 --> 00:25:28,680
[SPEAKER_00] jer smo tu na granici.

314
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] To sam te baš htjela bila.

315
00:25:30,579 --> 00:25:33,160
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ovako mala država na granici

316
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:36,039
[SPEAKER_01] koja je rekla s jednom prilikom

317
00:25:36,039 --> 00:25:37,819
[SPEAKER_01] da koja u stvari izgleda

318
00:25:37,819 --> 00:25:39,200
[SPEAKER_01] da će opet biti namijenjena

319
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:41,680
[SPEAKER_01] moderna uloga vojne krajne.

320
00:25:41,759 --> 00:25:43,839
[SPEAKER_01] vezano za ove sve migranske krize,

321
00:25:43,839 --> 00:25:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] tako je.

322
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:47,819
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ali što onda može uopće...

323
00:25:47,819 --> 00:25:50,839
[SPEAKER_01] Što može jedna ovakva mala Hrvatska,

324
00:25:50,839 --> 00:25:52,759
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, da ima najbolje vodstvo?

325
00:25:52,759 --> 00:25:53,880
[SPEAKER_01] Što bi mogla napraviti?

326
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pa može biti pametno i procjenjivati

327
00:25:55,579 --> 00:25:56,759
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je njezini interes.

328
00:25:56,759 --> 00:25:59,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ne slijediti slijepo nikoga,

329
00:25:59,259 --> 00:26:01,240
[SPEAKER_00] nego imati proaktivnu politiku.

330
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,779
[SPEAKER_00] A to možeš jedno...

331
00:26:02,779 --> 00:26:05,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti možeš nekome ponuditi nešto,

332
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:09,099
[SPEAKER_00] ti ne možeš tražiti od nekoga

333
00:26:09,099 --> 00:26:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] samo mi bismo to,

334
00:26:10,519 --> 00:26:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] dajte vi nas, zaštiti te, dajte...

335
00:26:12,279 --> 00:26:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ti moraš vidjeti gdje se to uklapa

336
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:15,700
[SPEAKER_00] u njihove interesi.

337
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] Sad vidim, mislim da se napokon shvaća

338
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] da ta priča, ono da se svodi

339
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] politika i zahtjevi u Bosni i Hercegovini

340
00:26:25,019 --> 00:26:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] na treći entitet,

341
00:26:26,319 --> 00:26:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] i to je nerealno.

342
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] To nije realno, to nema...

343
00:26:29,380 --> 00:26:31,940
[SPEAKER_00] Moraš naći načina na koji ćeš ti

344
00:26:31,940 --> 00:26:34,359
[SPEAKER_00] svoje interese zaštititi

345
00:26:34,359 --> 00:26:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] u sklopu nečijih većih interesa

346
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] i moraš pripoznati s kim to možeš napraviti.

347
00:26:40,619 --> 00:26:42,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da s Evropskom unijom

348
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] se nikad neće moći napraviti,

349
00:26:44,099 --> 00:26:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] a još manje će Hrvatska to moći

350
00:26:45,819 --> 00:26:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] s Rusijom ili s Turskom.

351
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:49,599
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ostaje onda kao onaj saviznik

352
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:51,720
[SPEAKER_01] i onaj koji nam je pomogao u konočnici

353
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] da oslobodimo svoje teritorije.

354
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:55,660
[SPEAKER_00] Koji uvijek može tu napraviti

355
00:26:55,660 --> 00:26:57,859
[SPEAKER_00] to nešto drugčije.

356
00:26:57,859 --> 00:26:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] Koji može prevaguju

357
00:26:58,940 --> 00:26:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] i koji će uvijek tu,

358
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:03,859
[SPEAKER_00] koliko god bilo posvećen

359
00:27:03,859 --> 00:27:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] drugim područjima.

360
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:07,660
[SPEAKER_00] Amerika može,

361
00:27:07,660 --> 00:27:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] koja je sad ugrožena,

362
00:27:09,319 --> 00:27:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] ja, snažno kinom,

363
00:27:11,559 --> 00:27:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali ona nema te sile koja...

364
00:27:15,039 --> 00:27:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Evropa nije ozbiljan faktor više,

365
00:27:17,559 --> 00:27:19,640
[SPEAKER_00] ali nema te sile koja

366
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] može biti dominirajuća u svijetu,

367
00:27:21,980 --> 00:27:24,279
[SPEAKER_00] a da nije dominirajuća i u Evropi.

368
00:27:24,559 --> 00:27:26,160
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je jedan nekakav spoj

369
00:27:26,160 --> 00:27:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] zajedničkih vrijednosti.

370
00:27:27,380 --> 00:27:28,799
[SPEAKER_00] Tu su mnoge razlike,

371
00:27:28,799 --> 00:27:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] tu su mnogi...

372
00:27:29,500 --> 00:27:29,839
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno.

373
00:27:29,839 --> 00:27:32,859
[SPEAKER_00] ne može se vezivati

374
00:27:32,859 --> 00:27:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] samo uz jednog partnera Evropska,

375
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:38,660
[SPEAKER_00] koristiti članstvo i razvijati

376
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] neke mogućnosti unutar Evropske unije

377
00:27:41,460 --> 00:27:44,200
[SPEAKER_00] svakako, jer to je bio cilj.

378
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] ali vidjeti što tko može učiniti

379
00:27:46,779 --> 00:27:49,180
[SPEAKER_00] i gdje je propoznati

380
00:27:49,180 --> 00:27:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] kako najlakša,

381
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:52,279
[SPEAKER_00] gdje su najveći potencijali

382
00:27:52,279 --> 00:27:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] za afirmirati vlastiti interes.

383
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:55,680
[SPEAKER_01] Na neki način,

384
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:56,720
[SPEAKER_01] sve ovo što si,

385
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] što si sad,

386
00:27:57,619 --> 00:27:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] meni je ovo toliko zanimljivo,

387
00:27:59,559 --> 00:28:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve što si sad iznjela je,

388
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:02,019
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način,

389
00:28:02,019 --> 00:28:05,019
[SPEAKER_01] to je kut iz kojeg si radila

390
00:28:05,019 --> 00:28:07,700
[SPEAKER_01] i svoj film o kardinalu Stepinzu,

391
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:09,259
[SPEAKER_01] koji će imati televizijsku premijeru,

392
00:28:09,259 --> 00:28:12,700
[SPEAKER_01] u srijedu 10. sad veljače

393
00:28:12,700 --> 00:28:14,519
[SPEAKER_01] u 20 sati.

394
00:28:14,519 --> 00:28:16,339
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, daj iz priče malo,

395
00:28:16,339 --> 00:28:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] reci mi o tom filmu,

396
00:28:18,039 --> 00:28:20,420
[SPEAKER_01] kako si ga ti posložila,

397
00:28:20,420 --> 00:28:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] te utjecaje,

398
00:28:21,539 --> 00:28:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] te odlične goste,

399
00:28:23,779 --> 00:28:25,299
[SPEAKER_01] ljude koji su u stvari,

400
00:28:25,299 --> 00:28:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] koje si uzela kao sugovornike.

401
00:28:27,539 --> 00:28:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] Na neki način si ga stavila,

402
00:28:30,380 --> 00:28:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] za mene izbijam,

403
00:28:31,940 --> 00:28:34,500
[SPEAKER_01] film taj bio iznenađenje

404
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:35,839
[SPEAKER_01] jer je potpuno drugačiji

405
00:28:35,839 --> 00:28:37,660
[SPEAKER_01] od drugih filmama koje sam bacio,

406
00:28:37,660 --> 00:28:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] potpuno jedno novo svjetlo,

407
00:28:39,059 --> 00:28:40,799
[SPEAKER_01] za mene na ulogu koju je imao

408
00:28:40,799 --> 00:28:41,720
[SPEAKER_01] kardinal Stepinac,

409
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:43,160
[SPEAKER_01] u stvari u vremenu u kojem je živio,

410
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:45,680
[SPEAKER_01] svjetsku ulogu koju je imao.

411
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa upravo ovo što si rekla,

412
00:28:47,619 --> 00:28:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] to je bio moj cilj.

413
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam željela napraviti film

414
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] o kardinalu Stepincu

415
00:28:54,759 --> 00:28:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam vidjela koliko zapravo

416
00:28:57,619 --> 00:28:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] ja malo o tome znam

417
00:28:58,559 --> 00:28:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] i koliko ga.

418
00:28:59,119 --> 00:29:01,359
[SPEAKER_00] Prije toga sam se ja bavila još

419
00:29:01,359 --> 00:29:04,839
[SPEAKER_00] istraživanjem zločina

420
00:29:04,839 --> 00:29:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] komunističkog režima

421
00:29:06,460 --> 00:29:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] nakon drugog svjetskog rata.

422
00:29:08,859 --> 00:29:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] pa kad je to,

423
00:29:11,140 --> 00:29:17,359
[SPEAKER_00] kad je taj ured koji je radio,

424
00:29:17,359 --> 00:29:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji je poznat ka ured profesora,

425
00:29:18,940 --> 00:29:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] jedno kratko vrijeme,

426
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:22,299
[SPEAKER_00] ali sam bila to ured koji je bio,

427
00:29:22,299 --> 00:29:24,019
[SPEAKER_00] koji je zaslugom

428
00:29:24,019 --> 00:29:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] najvećem profesora Hebranga osnovan

429
00:29:27,099 --> 00:29:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam tamo radila jedno vrijeme

430
00:29:30,500 --> 00:29:32,759
[SPEAKER_00] kao načelnica,

431
00:29:32,759 --> 00:29:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] poslije pred kraj sam bila i ravnateljca.

432
00:29:34,559 --> 00:29:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] U jednoj godini je žrtava grobnica.

433
00:29:38,059 --> 00:29:40,259
[SPEAKER_00] Grobnica komunističkog režima.

434
00:29:40,259 --> 00:29:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, to je bilo jedno isto sjajno iskustvo

435
00:29:44,180 --> 00:29:44,900
[SPEAKER_00] i sjajno razvoj.

436
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:47,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam te tu shvatila koliko zapravo

437
00:29:47,319 --> 00:29:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] smo mi bili društvo šutnje

438
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:53,660
[SPEAKER_00] i koliko toga se nije znalo

439
00:29:53,660 --> 00:29:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] i koliko je straha još i danas.

440
00:29:56,099 --> 00:29:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] u ljudima je bilo jedno fantastično iskustvo

441
00:29:59,099 --> 00:30:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] s profesorom Hebrangom

442
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:02,140
[SPEAKER_00] i upravnim viječem

443
00:30:02,140 --> 00:30:04,200
[SPEAKER_00] koje je bilo zaista sastavljeno

444
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] od 13 kompetentnih ljudi

445
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] iz institucija koje se time bave

446
00:30:07,980 --> 00:30:11,859
[SPEAKER_00] i koji su mogli dati svaki svoj doprinos

447
00:30:11,859 --> 00:30:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] i nije dugo trajalo.

448
00:30:13,039 --> 00:30:15,640
[SPEAKER_00] Na čemu to uvijek pukne na tome?

449
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako radiš pošteno,

450
00:30:17,519 --> 00:30:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] vidiš da zločin nije bio...

451
00:30:21,099 --> 00:30:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] Individualan.

452
00:30:23,079 --> 00:30:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Individualan, niti slučajan,

453
00:30:25,980 --> 00:30:27,779
[SPEAKER_00] niti da je zločin bio cilj,

454
00:30:27,779 --> 00:30:30,319
[SPEAKER_00] da je bio planski dio strukture

455
00:30:30,319 --> 00:30:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] i da je bila to planska likvidacija

456
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo građanske klase.

457
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] I to ne samo u Hrvatskoj,

458
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali u Hrvatskoj osobito.

459
00:30:37,900 --> 00:30:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga sam radila film

460
00:30:41,559 --> 00:30:42,900
[SPEAKER_00] Neprijatelj naroda.

461
00:30:42,900 --> 00:30:44,900
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, tako da ne ostane...

462
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

463
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da ostane zaokruženo i to razdoblje,

464
00:30:48,380 --> 00:30:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ne ispada,

465
00:30:49,000 --> 00:30:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] da ništa nismo uspjeli napraviti.

466
00:30:51,519 --> 00:30:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam napravila film

467
00:30:52,599 --> 00:30:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] i tu sam se zapravo osrela po prvi put

468
00:30:55,859 --> 00:31:00,200
[SPEAKER_00] s pričom o Kardinalu Stepincu

469
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovoj ulozi

470
00:31:01,099 --> 00:31:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] i odlučila sam napraviti sljedeći film o njemu.

471
00:31:04,539 --> 00:31:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je to išlo.

472
00:31:05,960 --> 00:31:07,799
[SPEAKER_01] Da treba nosanemo na neprijatelju naroda,

473
00:31:07,799 --> 00:31:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] ova šutnja koju govoriš,

474
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,160
[SPEAKER_01] da te iznenadilo,

475
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:13,819
[SPEAKER_01] da i danas ta šutnja

476
00:31:13,819 --> 00:31:16,019
[SPEAKER_01] postoji strah u ljudima

477
00:31:16,019 --> 00:31:17,740
[SPEAKER_01] kad govore o komunističkim zločinima.

478
00:31:17,740 --> 00:31:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pa danas, pa ljudi su...

479
00:31:20,079 --> 00:31:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je potesan ta šutnja.

480
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] 5 km od Velike Gorice.

481
00:31:25,119 --> 00:31:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ti imaš ljude koji se nisu...

482
00:31:26,859 --> 00:31:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi put bi govorili,

483
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,400
[SPEAKER_00] drugi put se nisu usudili govoriti

484
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] da ih ne pojede noć.

485
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] I onda nakon 3 godine

486
00:31:33,839 --> 00:31:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] ti shvatiš da su možda oni bili u pravu.

487
00:31:35,940 --> 00:31:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] To danas to...

488
00:31:36,980 --> 00:31:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudima koji se nisu s tim susretali...

489
00:31:39,980 --> 00:31:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] Zvuči kao nevjerojatno.

490
00:31:42,180 --> 00:31:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi koji se boje za posao,

491
00:31:45,980 --> 00:31:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] za napredovanje svoje djece.

492
00:31:49,019 --> 00:31:50,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim, djeca već imaju 50 godina.

493
00:31:50,740 --> 00:31:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ali oni se boje za...

494
00:31:52,359 --> 00:31:55,680
[SPEAKER_01] Boje se jer su i druga djeca i unuci u sustav.

495
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:59,140
[SPEAKER_00] I onda vidiš da su...

496
00:31:59,140 --> 00:32:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] Da je dosta toga izmanipulirano

497
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] u tim policijskim istragama,

498
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:04,799
[SPEAKER_00] da su podmetnuti neki dokazi.

499
00:32:04,799 --> 00:32:06,259
[SPEAKER_00] Tako vidiš da je zapravo

500
00:32:06,259 --> 00:32:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] taj stari sustav ušao

501
00:32:08,119 --> 00:32:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] i u tu sferu istraživanja

502
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] i da zapravo se čini sve

503
00:32:12,059 --> 00:32:14,880
